item.title: By: Jo El Snyder
item.dc:creator: Jo El Snyder
item.description: I went to Seven Wonders when I was a student at JU. They had the BEST coffee con leche and fruit filed empadanas. I had often wondered if they were still open. Good luck to Bonnie Kilgore-Conde to reopening a BADLY needed high point for the JU area.
